sentences: Vidar Busk (born 19 May 1970 in Langesund, Norway) is a Norwegian guitarist, vocalist, composer and record producer within genres blues and soul.
He toured the U.S. several years before returning to Norway in 1990, and was awarded Smugetprisen 1994.
